{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8b6c192674","title":"李德日记摘要","origin":"中国人民大学经济系政治经济学教研室编《中国资產阶级右派经济言论批判参考资料》，1958年9月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9c7ed909b2","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"8b6c192674"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"018b7bda33","name":"李德"},{"id":"0389fdf66c","name":"中國人民大學"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ecbd1324b3","type":"title","text":"李德日记摘要","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8b6c192674"},{"id":"c19794765e","type":"authors","text":"中國人民大學李德","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8b6c192674"},{"id":"3dc2a83cf5","type":"subtitle","text":"（李德：中国人民大学哲学系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8b6c192674"},{"id":"f1f4bf0852","type":"paragraph","text":"几天的活动，我得出下列结论：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8b6c192674"},{"id":"b1bf42d84b","type":"paragraph","text":"1.必须推翻现有制度，代替以更新的社会，但决不是私有制的资本主义。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8b6c192674"},{"id":"418e2346bf","type":"paragraph","text":"2.必须消灭党，永远消灭党！这是事情成功的根源，也是事情失败的根源。当组织力量反对现实时，需要党，当新的社会已产生，需要人民自己来做。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8b6c192674"},{"id":"e2c8646082","type":"paragraph","text":"3.必须从理论上证明这是真理，真理的解释世界，合理的创造世界。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8b6c192674"},{"id":"a36d1634a8","type":"appellation","text":"（摘自“哲学系学生李德日记摘要”。载《社会主义思想教育参考资料选辑》第四辑，第224页）","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8b6c192674"}],"page":{"id":"e4416cefb2","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8b6c192674","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}